- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): The paper discusses the use of logical reasoning and equational proofs to verify programs, which is related to logic in computer science.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper presents a technique for verifying software correctness, which is related to software engineering.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory): The paper uses techniques from model checking and abstract interpretation, which are related to formal languages and automata theory.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): Although not the main focus of the paper, the use of automated proof-search algorithms could be related to machine learning.
